data.description: Fuqua Good Cents energy efficient home. Has certified wood stove, vaulted ceilings and in move-in condition. Owner will leave all appliances including washer/dryer. Owner has spent lots of money on fencing and items for horses. Detached double garage with shop area plus storage shed with wood storage. Fully fenced corner lot on paved road with decks front and back. Very nice property.
